quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  75,31,Por li observ nek charity nor kontakt prayers (Salat)
  75,32,Li disbelieved torn
  75,33,Kun his famili li akt arrogantly
  75,34,Vi ind this
  75,35,Ja vi ind this
  75,36,human est opini li ir nothing
  75,37,Li ne gut est ejected semen
  75,38,Tiam Li kre embryo gxi
  75,39,Li far gxi vir female
  75,40,Li est tiam unable revive dead